org.pepstock.charba.client.options

Class AbstractModel<P extends AbstractModel<?,?>,D>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pepstock.charba.client.commons.NativeObjectContainer
      • org.pepstock.charba.client.options.AbstractModel<P,D>
  • Type Parameters:
    P - parent node class
    D - defaults provider class
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractElement, AngleLines, Animation, DisplayFormats, Elements, FontItem, GridLines, Hover, Layout, Legend, Options, Padding, Plugins, Scale, ScaleLabelPadding, Scales, Time, Tooltips, TooltipsCallbacks

    public abstract class AbstractModel<P extends AbstractModel<?,?>,D>
extends NativeObjectContainer
    Base class for all options, which will wraps a native object and manages the relations about parent and children elements.
    Provides also a set of methods to manages callbacks and events.
    Author:
    Andrea "Stock" Stocchero
